highlights.text: “Ram Pam Pam” by Natti Natasha and Becky G is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 51 spots at #97.
“Qué Más Pues?” by J Balvin and Maria Becerra is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #77.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 226 weeks straight.
Olivia Rodrigo has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “good 4 u” is the highest at #1.
